HotLinks Developers Kit         4/28/92

This is the HotLinks Developers Kit we are making available to any 
and all who are interested in adding hotlinks support to their 
applications (present or future).

Please read all the documentation in the 'docs' drawer, especially the
'What_Is_HotLinks.text' and the 'IFF_DOC.text' as these contain important
information relating to HotLinks.

For more information contact Dan Weiss at Soft-Logik.
        
